7 A Joint Resolution approving certain proposed
permanent major rules of the Oklahoma Health Care
8 Authority; and directing distribution.
9
10
11 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
12 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a separate
13 joint resolution to approve or disapprove major rules.
14 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
15 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
16 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves all the following
17 proposed major rules submitted by the Oklahoma Health Care Authority
18 on or before February 1, 2026: OAC 317:30-5-47 and 317:30-5-47.7.
19 SECTION 2. The Oklahoma Secretary of State is hereby directed
20 to distribute copies of this resolution to the Governor and the
21 editor of "The Oklahoma Register".
